(1, 5, 'RFID-Card', 'The RFID PVC Card - Standard is a high-quality identification card embedded with RFID technology for secure access control and identification purposes. This card is manufactured using premium PVC material that ensures durability and longevity. The card features a standard CR80 size (85.6mm x 54mm) that fits perfectly in wallets and card holders. The embedded RFID chip allows for contactless reading, making it ideal for access control systems, employee identification, student ID cards, and membership cards. The card surface is printable on both sides using standard card printers, allowing for customization with logos, photos, and text. The PVC material provides resistance to wear and tear, ensuring the card maintains its appearance and functionality over extended use.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: High-grade PVC (Polyvinyl Chloride)\r\n- Technology: Embedded RFID chip (13.56MHz or 125kHz frequency)\r\n- Dimensions: CR80 standard (85.6mm x 54mm x 0.76mm)\r\n- Print Area: Full surface printable on both sides\r\n- Operating Temperature: -20°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -30°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: 10% to 90% non-condensing\r\n- Read Distance: 0-10cm (depending on reader)\r\n- Memory Capacity: 1KB to 4KB (varies by chip type)\r\n- Data Retention: Up to 10 years\r\n- Write Cycles: Minimum 100,000 cycles\r\n- Compatibility: Works with most standard RFID readers\r\n- Security Features: Password protection, data encryption capabilities\r\n- Standards Compliance: ISO/IEC 14443, ISO/IEC 15693 (depending on chip)', 120.00, 'id-card-rfid-pvc.png', '2025-10-08 00:21:44', '2025-11-17 00:16:14'),
(2, 5, 'PVC Card', 'The PVC Card is a premium quality identification card made from high-grade polyvinyl chloride (PVC) material, offering excellent durability and professional appearance. This standard CR80 sized card (85.6mm x 54mm) is ideal for employee ID cards, student identification, membership cards, and access control applications. The card features a smooth, glossy surface that accepts high-quality printing using standard card printers, dye-sublimation printers, or laser engraving equipment. The PVC material is resistant to bending, scratching, and fading, ensuring long-lasting performance in daily use. With its professional look and feel, this card is perfect for organizations that want to present a polished image while providing reliable identification solutions. The card can be customized with full-color graphics, photos, barcodes, and magnetic stripes upon request.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: High-grade PVC (Polyvinyl Chloride)\r\n- Dimensions: CR80 standard (85.6mm x 54mm x 0.76mm)\r\n- Thickness: 0.76mm (30 mil)\r\n- Surface Finish: Glossy on both sides\r\n- Print Compatibility: Compatible with direct-to-card and retransfer printers\r\n- Operating Temperature: -20°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -30°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: 10% to 90% non-condensing\r\n- Durability: Resistant to bending, scratching, and fading\r\n- Print Area: Full surface coverage on both sides\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: ISO/IEC 7810 ID-1 format\r\n- Optional Features: Magnetic stripe, barcode, holographic overlay available\r\n- Lifespan: 3-5 years under normal usage conditions', 100.00, 'id-card-pvc.png', '2025-10-08 00:21:44', '2025-11-17 00:16:14'),
(3, 2, 'Polyester Lanyards', 'Our Polyester Lanyards are premium quality identification accessories made from durable polyester material that offers excellent color retention and long-lasting performance. These lanyards feature a smooth, soft texture that is comfortable to wear while providing superior strength and resistance to fraying. The polyester material is ideal for sublimation printing, allowing for vibrant, full-color designs that won\'t fade or crack over time. With a standard width of 20mm and adjustable length, these lanyards are perfect for employee ID cards, visitor passes, and event badges. The durable construction ensures they can withstand daily use in various environments, from corporate offices to industrial settings. Available with various attachment options including breakaway clips, lobster clasps, and metal swivels for added safety and convenience.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: High-quality polyester fabric\r\n- Width: 20mm (standard), custom widths available\r\n- Length: 900mm (adjustable), custom lengths available\r\n- Printing Method: Sublimation printing for vibrant colors\r\n- Color Fastness: Excellent fade resistance\r\n- Durability: Resistant to fraying and wear\r\n- Attachment Options: Breakaway clip, lobster clasp, metal swivel\r\n- Safety Features: Breakaway release mechanism available\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Washability: Hand wash recommended\r\n- Edge Finish: Heat-sealed edges to prevent fraying\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general textile accessory standards\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, custom sizes, logo placement', 40.00, 'lanyard-polyester.png', '2025-10-08 00:21:44', '2025-11-17 00:24:28'),
(4, 5, 'Pouch Card', 'The Pouch Card is a versatile identification solution that combines the durability of a protective pouch with the convenience of a standard card format. This innovative design features a clear PVC pouch that securely holds a standard CR80 card (85.6mm x 54mm) while providing additional protection against wear, moisture, and damage. The pouch design allows for easy insertion and replacement of identification cards, making it ideal for temporary IDs, visitor passes, and multi-purpose access cards. The clear pouch material ensures complete visibility of the enclosed card while offering protection from bending, scratching, and environmental factors. The card can be easily attached to lanyards, keychains, or badges using the integrated attachment points. This solution is perfect for organizations that require flexible identification systems with the ability to update or change cards as needed without replacing the entire ID system.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Pouch Material: Clear PVC or PETG\r\n- Card Compatibility: Standard CR80 size (85.6mm x 54mm)\r\n- Pouch Dimensions: 90mm x 60mm (with sealing margin)\r\n- Thickness: 0.5mm pouch material\r\n- Attachment Options: Lanyard hole, keychain loop, clip attachment\r\n- Print Area: Full visibility of enclosed card\r\n- Durability: Water-resistant and tear-resistant\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +60°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 80% non-condensing\r\n- Security Features: Tamper-evident sealing options\r\n- Edge Quality: Heat-sealed edges for durability\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general ID card standards\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Available in different colors and sizes', 80.00, 'id-card-pouch.png', '2025-11-16 21:33:30', '2025-11-17 00:24:28'),
(5, 3, 'Plastic Badge - 75x50mm', 'The Plastic Badge - 75x50mm is a durable and professional identification solution designed for temporary or permanent use in various environments. This badge features a sturdy plastic construction that resists bending, cracking, and fading, ensuring long-lasting performance. The compact 75x50mm size makes it ideal for attaching to uniforms, clothing, or lanyards while maintaining visibility. The smooth surface accepts high-quality printing, allowing for clear text, logos, and graphics that enhance your organization\'s professional image. With its lightweight design and secure attachment options, this badge is perfect for employee identification, visitor passes, and event credentials. The plastic material is easy to clean and maintain, making it suitable for use in healthcare, hospitality, retail, and industrial settings. Available with various attachment methods including clips, pins, and magnetic backs for versatile application.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: Durable plastic (PVC or ABS)\r\n- Dimensions: 75mm x 50mm x 2mm\r\n- Thickness: 2mm standard\r\n- Surface Finish: Smooth, printable surface\r\n- Print Area: Full surface coverage\r\n- Print Compatibility: Compatible with standard badge printers\r\n- Attachment Options: Clip, pin, magnetic back available\r\n- Durability: Resistant to bending, cracking, and fading\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 85% non-condensing\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general badge standards\r\n- Lifespan: 1-2 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, custom shapes available', 35.00, 'badge-plastic.png', '2025-10-08 00:21:44', '2025-11-17 00:33:38'),
(6, 3, 'Metal Badge - Premium', 'The Metal Badge - Premium is a high-quality identification solution crafted from durable metal materials for a professional and prestigious appearance. This badge features a sleek, polished finish that exudes quality and sophistication, making it ideal for executive identification, security personnel, and premium membership cards. The robust metal construction ensures exceptional durability and longevity, withstanding daily wear and tear in demanding environments. The badge can be customized with engraved text, logos, and intricate designs that maintain their clarity and sharpness over time. With its substantial weight and premium feel, this badge conveys authority and professionalism. The metal surface can be finished in various options including brushed, polished, or matte finishes to suit your organization\'s aesthetic preferences. Perfect for corporate executives, security personnel, military applications, and high-end membership programs where a premium identification solution is required.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: High-grade metal (stainless steel, brass, or aluminum)\r\n- Dimensions: 75mm x 50mm x 3mm (standard)\r\n- Thickness: 3mm standard\r\n- Surface Finish: Brushed, polished, or matte options\r\n- Engraving Method: Laser engraving or chemical etching\r\n- Attachment Options: Pin, clip, or chain attachment\r\n- Durability: Exceptional resistance to wear and corrosion\r\n- Operating Temperature: -20°C to +80°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -30°C to +90°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 95% non-condensing\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with polished edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets premium badge standards\r\n- Lifespan: 5-10 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Engraved text, logos, custom shapes available\r\n- Special Features: Color-fill options for engraved areas', 150.00, 'badge-metal.png', '2025-10-08 00:21:44', '2025-11-17 00:36:12'),
(7, 2, 'Nylon Lanyards', 'Our Nylon Lanyards are premium quality identification accessories made from strong and durable nylon material that offers excellent strength and longevity. These lanyards feature a smooth, soft texture that is comfortable to wear while providing superior durability and resistance to fraying. The nylon material is ideal for sublimation printing, allowing for vibrant, full-color designs that won\'t fade or crack over time. With a standard width of 20mm and adjustable length, these lanyards are perfect for employee ID cards, visitor passes, and event badges. The durable construction ensures they can withstand daily use in various environments, from corporate offices to industrial settings. Available with various attachment options including breakaway clips, lobster clasps, and metal swivels for added safety and convenience. The nylon fabric is lightweight yet strong, making it an excellent choice for extended wear without discomfort.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: High-quality nylon fabric\r\n- Width: 20mm (standard), custom widths available\r\n- Length: 900mm (adjustable), custom lengths available\r\n- Printing Method: Sublimation printing for vibrant colors\r\n- Color Fastness: Excellent fade resistance\r\n- Durability: Resistant to fraying and wear\r\n- Attachment Options: Breakaway clip, lobster clasp, metal swivel\r\n- Safety Features: Breakaway release mechanism available\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Washability: Hand wash recommended\r\n- Edge Finish: Heat-sealed edges to prevent fraying\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general textile accessory standards\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, custom sizes, logo placement', 45.00, 'lanyard-nylon.png', '2025-11-16 21:38:03', '2025-11-17 00:37:46'),
(8, 2, 'Lanyard Prints', 'Our Lanyard Prints service offers custom-designed lanyards with high-quality printing to showcase your brand, logo, or message with vibrant colors and sharp details. These printed lanyards are made from premium polyester or nylon material that ensures durability and long-lasting performance. Using advanced sublimation printing technology, we create full-color designs that won\'t fade, crack, or peel over time, even with regular use and washing. Our printing process allows for complete customization, including your company logo, tagline, artwork, or any graphics that represent your brand identity. The lanyards feature a smooth, soft texture that is comfortable to wear while providing superior strength and resistance to fraying. With a standard width of 20mm and adjustable length, these printed lanyards are perfect for employee ID cards, visitor passes, event badges, and promotional giveaways. Available with various attachment options including breakaway clips, lobster clasps, and metal swivels for added safety and convenience.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: High-quality polyester or nylon fabric\r\n- Width: 20mm (standard), custom widths available\r\n- Length: 900mm (adjustable), custom lengths available\r\n- Printing Method: Sublimation printing for vibrant colors\r\n- Color Fastness: Excellent fade resistance\r\n- Durability: Resistant to fraying and wear\r\n- Attachment Options: Breakaway clip, lobster clasp, metal swivel\r\n- Safety Features: Breakaway release mechanism available\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Washability: Hand wash recommended\r\n- Edge Finish: Heat-sealed edges to prevent fraying\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general textile accessory standards\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, custom sizes, logo placement', 60.00, 'lanyard-printed.png', '2025-11-16 21:38:03', '2025-11-17 00:39:10'),
(9, 2, 'Customized Lanyards', 'Our Customized Lanyards service provides fully personalized lanyard solutions tailored to your specific requirements and brand identity. These custom lanyards are crafted from premium quality polyester or nylon material, ensuring durability and long-lasting performance. We offer complete customization options including unique shapes, sizes, colors, and printing designs to perfectly match your organization\'s aesthetic and functional needs. Using advanced sublimation printing technology, we create vibrant, high-resolution designs that won\'t fade, crack, or peel over time, even with regular use and washing. Our custom lanyards can feature your company logo, tagline, artwork, or any graphics that represent your brand identity. With various width options from 10mm to 25mm and adjustable lengths, these lanyards are perfect for employee ID cards, visitor passes, event badges, and promotional giveaways. Available with a wide range of attachment options including breakaway clips, lobster clasps, metal swivels, and custom hardware for added safety and convenience. Our design team works closely with you to create the perfect lanyard that meets your exact specifications.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: High-quality polyester or nylon fabric\r\n- Width: 10mm to 25mm (customizable), standard 20mm\r\n- Length: 800mm to 1000mm (customizable), standard 900mm\r\n- Printing Method: Sublimation printing for vibrant colors\r\n- Color Fastness: Excellent fade resistance\r\n- Durability: Resistant to fraying and wear\r\n- Attachment Options: Breakaway clip, lobster clasp, metal swivel, custom hardware\r\n- Safety Features: Breakaway release mechanism available\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Washability: Hand wash recommended\r\n- Edge Finish: Heat-sealed edges to prevent fraying\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general textile accessory standards\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, custom sizes, shapes, logo placement', 65.00, 'lanyard-customized.png', '2025-11-16 21:38:03', '2025-11-17 00:40:34'),
(11, 1, 'RFID Attendance Machine', 'The RFID Attendance Machine is a sophisticated access control and time tracking solution designed for efficient employee attendance management in corporate offices, schools, and industrial environments. This advanced system utilizes RFID technology to accurately record employee check-ins and check-outs with minimal effort and maximum precision. The machine features a high-sensitivity RFID reader that can quickly scan RFID cards, tags, or badges from a distance of up to 10cm, ensuring fast and reliable identification. With its robust construction and weather-resistant design, this attendance machine is suitable for both indoor and outdoor installations. The device includes a clear LCD display that shows real-time information including employee ID, time, and date, providing immediate feedback to users. The system can store thousands of attendance records internally and can be easily connected to a computer via USB or network connection for data transfer and management. With its user-friendly interface and simple operation, employees can quickly scan their RFID cards to clock in or out, reducing queue times and improving workplace efficiency.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Technology: 13.56MHz or 125kHz RFID reader\r\n- Reading Distance: 0-10cm (depending on card type)\r\n- Display: LCD screen for real-time information\r\n- Storage Capacity: Up to 100,000 records\r\n- Communication: USB, Ethernet, or Wi-Fi connectivity\r\n- Power Supply: 12V DC adapter or battery backup\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: 10% to 90% non-condensing\r\n- Dimensions: 200mm x 120mm x 40mm\r\n- Weight: 500g (excluding accessories)\r\n- Mounting Options: Wall mount or stand mount\r\n- Security Features: Password protection, data encryption\r\n- Standards Compliance: ISO/IEC 14443, ISO/IEC 15693\r\n- Lifespan: 5-7 years under normal usage conditions', 6499.00, 'attendance-rfid-machine.png', '2025-10-16 03:50:36', '2025-11-17 00:42:51'),
(12, 1, 'Face Recognition Machine', 'The Face Recognition Machine is an advanced biometric identification and access control solution that utilizes cutting-edge facial recognition technology for secure and contactless identification. This intelligent system employs high-resolution cameras and sophisticated AI algorithms to accurately identify individuals by analyzing unique facial features and characteristics. The machine features a high-sensitivity camera with infrared capabilities that ensures accurate recognition even in low-light conditions or complete darkness. With its fast processing speed, the system can identify individuals within seconds, making it ideal for high-traffic environments such as office buildings, schools, and residential complexes. The device includes a clear LCD touchscreen display that provides real-time feedback and user interaction, allowing for easy navigation and system management. The system can store thousands of facial templates securely and can be easily connected to a computer or network for data transfer and management. With its touchless operation, this face recognition machine provides a hygienic and convenient solution for access control, attendance tracking, and security monitoring. The system also includes advanced anti-spoofing technology to prevent unauthorized access using photographs or videos.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Technology: AI-based facial recognition with 3D depth sensing\r\n- Camera Resolution: 2MP HD camera with infrared capabilities\r\n- Recognition Speed: Less than 1 second\r\n- Recognition Accuracy: 99.5% accuracy rate\r\n- Storage Capacity: Up to 50,000 facial templates\r\n- Communication: USB, Ethernet, or Wi-Fi connectivity\r\n- Power Supply: 12V DC adapter\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +60°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: 10% to 80% non-condensing\r\n- Dimensions: 180mm x 120mm x 45mm\r\n- Weight: 600g (excluding accessories)\r\n- Display: 4.3-inch LCD touchscreen\r\n- Security Features: Anti-spoofing technology, data encryption\r\n- Standards Compliance: ISO/IEC 30107-3, ISO/IEC 27001\r\n- Lifespan: 5-7 years under normal usage conditions', 9999.00, 'attendance-face-id-machine.png', '2025-10-16 03:50:36', '2025-11-17 00:44:28'),
(13, 1, 'Fingerprint Scanner Unit', 'The Fingerprint Scanner Unit is a reliable biometric identification and access control solution that utilizes advanced fingerprint recognition technology for secure and efficient identification. This sophisticated system employs high-resolution optical or capacitive sensors to accurately capture and analyze unique fingerprint patterns for precise identification. The scanner features a durable construction with a scratch-resistant sensing surface that ensures long-lasting performance and consistent accuracy. With its fast processing speed, the system can authenticate individuals within seconds, making it ideal for high-traffic environments such as office buildings, data centers, and restricted access areas. The device includes clear LED indicators that provide real-time feedback during the scanning process, ensuring users know when to place their finger and when authentication is complete. The system can store thousands of fingerprint templates securely and can be easily connected to a computer or access control system via USB or network connection for seamless integration. With its touch-based operation, this fingerprint scanner provides a hygienic and convenient solution for access control, time attendance tracking, and security monitoring. The system also includes advanced anti-spoofing technology to prevent unauthorized access using artificial fingerprints or photographs.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Technology: Optical or capacitive fingerprint sensor\r\n- Sensor Resolution: 500 DPI high-resolution scanning\r\n- Scanning Speed: Less than 1 second\r\n- Recognition Accuracy: 99.5% accuracy rate\r\n- Storage Capacity: Up to 3,000 fingerprint templates\r\n- Communication: USB, RS232, or Wi-Fi connectivity\r\n- Power Supply: 5V DC via USB or 12V DC adapter\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +60°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: 10% to 80% non-condensing\r\n- Dimensions: 150mm x 100mm x 40mm\r\n- Weight: 400g (excluding accessories)\r\n- Indicator: LED status indicators for feedback\r\n- Security Features: Anti-spoofing technology, data encryption\r\n- Standards Compliance: ISO/IEC 19794-2, ISO/IEC 27001\r\n- Lifespan: 5-7 years under normal usage conditions', 4999.00, 'attendance-fingerprint-machine.png', '2025-10-16 03:50:36', '2025-11-17 00:46:43'),
(14, 1, 'QR/Barcode Scanner', 'The QR/Barcode Scanner is a versatile and efficient identification and data capture solution designed for quick and accurate scanning of QR codes and barcodes. This advanced scanning device utilizes high-resolution imaging technology and sophisticated decoding algorithms to rapidly read various types of 1D and 2D codes, including QR codes, Data Matrix, PDF417, and traditional barcodes. The scanner features a durable construction with an ergonomic design that ensures comfortable handling during extended use periods. With its fast scanning speed, the system can decode codes within milliseconds, making it ideal for retail environments, inventory management, access control, and asset tracking applications. The device includes clear LED indicators and audible feedback that provide real-time confirmation when codes are successfully scanned. The system can be easily connected to a computer or mobile device via USB or wireless connectivity options for seamless data transfer and integration with existing software systems. With its plug-and-play operation, this QR/Barcode scanner provides a convenient solution for point-of-sale transactions, inventory management, visitor registration, and security monitoring. The scanner also includes advanced error correction technology to ensure accurate reading even from damaged or poorly printed codes.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Technology: 1D and 2D barcode scanning with CMOS sensor\r\n- Scan Speed: Up to 100 scans per second\r\n- Scan Distance: 50mm to 200mm (varies by code type)\r\n- Supported Codes: QR Code, Data Matrix, PDF417, Code 128, EAN-13, UPC-A, and more\r\n- Decoding Accuracy: 99.9% accuracy rate\r\n- Communication: USB, Bluetooth, or Wi-Fi connectivity\r\n- Power Supply: 5V DC via USB or internal rechargeable battery\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +60°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: 10% to 80% non-condensing\r\n- Dimensions: 160mm x 70mm x 40mm\r\n- Weight: 150g (excluding accessories)\r\n- Indicator: LED status indicators and buzzer feedback\r\n- Security Features: Data encryption, secure communication protocols\r\n- Standards Compliance: ISO/IEC 15415, ISO/IEC 15416\r\n- Lifespan: 3-5 years under normal usage conditions', 2500.00, 'attendance-qr-scanner.png', '2025-10-16 03:50:36', '2025-11-17 00:48:28'),
(15, 5, 'PVC Card - Standard', 'The UV-Card is a premium identification solution that utilizes advanced UV printing technology to create vibrant, high-resolution images with exceptional durability. This card is manufactured using high-quality PVC material and features full-color UV printing that produces sharp text, vivid graphics, and detailed photographs with fade-resistant inks. The UV printing process embeds the image directly into the card surface, making it highly resistant to scratching, fading, and wear. The card maintains a professional appearance over extended use, making it ideal for employee ID cards, membership cards, and access control applications. The UV printing technology allows for edge-to-edge printing coverage, ensuring maximum visual impact. With its superior print quality and long-lasting durability, the UV-Card is perfect for organizations that require premium identification solutions with a polished, professional look.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Printing Technology: UV direct-to-card printing\r\n- Material: High-grade PVC (Polyvinyl Chloride)\r\n- Dimensions: CR80 standard (85.6mm x 54mm x 0.76mm)\r\n- Print Resolution: Up to 1200 DPI\r\n- Print Area: Full surface coverage (edge-to-edge)\r\n- Color Depth: 24-bit color (16.7 million colors)\r\n- Surface Finish: Glossy or matte options available\r\n- Durability: Scratch-resistant UV coating\r\n- Fade Resistance: Excellent UV stability\r\n- Operating Temperature: -20°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -30°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: 10% to 90% non-condensing\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: ISO/IEC 7810 ID-1 format\r\n- Lifespan: 5-7 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Special Features: Holographic overlay options available', 100.00, 'id-card-pvc.png', '2025-11-16 21:25:39', '2025-11-17 00:24:28'),
(16, 5, 'Pouch Card', 'The Pouch Card is a versatile identification solution that combines the durability of a protective pouch with the convenience of a standard card format. This innovative design features a clear PVC pouch that securely holds a standard CR80 card (85.6mm x 54mm) while providing additional protection against wear, moisture, and damage. The pouch design allows for easy insertion and replacement of identification cards, making it ideal for temporary IDs, visitor passes, and multi-purpose access cards. The clear pouch material ensures complete visibility of the enclosed card while offering protection from bending, scratching, and environmental factors. The card can be easily attached to lanyards, keychains, or badges using the integrated attachment points. This solution is perfect for organizations that require flexible identification systems with the ability to update or change cards as needed without replacing the entire ID system.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Pouch Material: Clear PVC or PETG\r\n- Card Compatibility: Standard CR80 size (85.6mm x 54mm)\r\n- Pouch Dimensions: 90mm x 60mm (with sealing margin)\r\n- Thickness: 0.5mm pouch material\r\n- Attachment Options: Lanyard hole, keychain loop, clip attachment\r\n- Print Area: Full visibility of enclosed card\r\n- Durability: Water-resistant and tear-resistant\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +60°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 80% non-condensing\r\n- Security Features: Tamper-evident sealing options\r\n- Edge Quality: Heat-sealed edges for durability\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general ID card standards\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Available in different colors and sizes', 80.00, 'id-card-pouch.png', '2025-11-16 21:25:39', '2025-11-17 00:57:11'),
(17, NULL, 'Nylon Lanyard - 20mm', 'The Nylon Lanyard - 20mm is a premium quality identification accessory made from strong and durable nylon material that offers excellent strength and longevity. This lanyard features a smooth, soft texture that is comfortable to wear while providing superior durability and resistance to fraying. The standard 20mm width is ideal for sublimation printing, allowing for vibrant, full-color designs that won\'t fade or crack over time. With an adjustable length, this lanyard is perfect for employee ID cards, visitor passes, and event badges. The durable construction ensures it can withstand daily use in various environments, from corporate offices to industrial settings. Available with various attachment options including breakaway clips, lobster clasps, and metal swivels for added safety and convenience. The nylon fabric is lightweight yet strong, making it an excellent choice for extended wear without discomfort.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: High-quality nylon fabric\r\n- Width: 20mm (standard)\r\n- Length: 900mm (adjustable)\r\n- Printing Method: Sublimation printing for vibrant colors\r\n- Color Fastness: Excellent fade resistance\r\n- Durability: Resistant to fraying and wear\r\n- Attachment Options: Breakaway clip, lobster clasp, metal swivel\r\n- Safety Features: Breakaway release mechanism available\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Washability: Hand wash recommended\r\n- Edge Finish: Heat-sealed edges to prevent fraying\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general textile accessory standards\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions', 45.00, 'lanyard_poly.png', '2025-11-16 21:25:39', '2025-11-17 00:59:40'),
(18, NULL, 'Printed Lanyard - Custom', 'The Printed Lanyard - Custom is a premium identification accessory that features high-quality custom printing to showcase your brand, logo, or message with vibrant colors and sharp details. This printed lanyard is made from premium polyester or nylon material that ensures durability and long-lasting performance. Using advanced sublimation printing technology, we create full-color designs that won\'t fade, crack, or peel over time, even with regular use and washing. Our printing process allows for complete customization, including your company logo, tagline, artwork, or any graphics that represent your brand identity. The lanyard features a smooth, soft texture that is comfortable to wear while providing superior strength and resistance to fraying. With a standard width of 20mm and adjustable length, this printed lanyard is perfect for employee ID cards, visitor passes, event badges, and promotional giveaways. Available with various attachment options including breakaway clips, lobster clasps, and metal swivels for added safety and convenience.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: High-quality polyester or nylon fabric\r\n- Width: 20mm (standard)\r\n- Length: 900mm (adjustable)\r\n- Printing Method: Sublimation printing for vibrant colors\r\n- Color Fastness: Excellent fade resistance\r\n- Durability: Resistant to fraying and wear\r\n- Attachment Options: Breakaway clip, lobster clasp, metal swivel\r\n- Safety Features: Breakaway release mechanism available\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Washability: Hand wash recommended\r\n- Edge Finish: Heat-sealed edges to prevent fraying\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general textile accessory standards\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, logo placement', 60.00, 'lanyard_print.png', '2025-11-16 21:25:39', '2025-11-17 00:59:40'),
(19, 3, 'Clip Badge - Reusable', 'The Clip Badge - Reusable is a versatile and durable identification solution designed for temporary or permanent use in various environments. This badge features a sturdy plastic construction with a reusable clip mechanism that allows for easy attachment and removal from clothing, uniforms, or lanyards. The compact design makes it ideal for visitor passes, event credentials, and temporary identification needs. The smooth surface accepts high-quality printing, allowing for clear text, logos, and graphics that enhance your organization\'s professional image. With its lightweight design and secure clip attachment, this badge is perfect for situations where quick and easy identification is needed. The plastic material is easy to clean and maintain, making it suitable for use in healthcare, hospitality, retail, and industrial settings. The reusable design makes it an economical choice for organizations that need temporary identification solutions.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: Durable plastic (PVC or ABS)\r\n- Dimensions: 75mm x 50mm x 2mm\r\n- Thickness: 2mm standard\r\n- Surface Finish: Smooth, printable surface\r\n- Print Area: Full surface coverage\r\n- Print Compatibility: Compatible with standard badge printers\r\n- Attachment Options: Reusable clip mechanism\r\n- Durability: Resistant to bending, cracking, and fading\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 85% non-condensing\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general badge standards\r\n- Lifespan: 1-2 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, custom shapes available', 25.00, 'badge-clip.png', '2025-11-16 21:25:39', '2025-11-17 00:59:40'),
(20, 3, 'Magnetic Badge - Strong Hold', 'The Magnetic Badge - Strong Hold is a premium identification solution that utilizes a powerful magnetic attachment system for secure and convenient wear. This badge features a sturdy plastic construction with a strong magnetic backing that provides a reliable hold to metal surfaces while allowing for easy removal when needed. The compact 75x50mm size makes it ideal for employee identification, visitor passes, and event credentials. The smooth surface accepts high-quality printing, allowing for clear text, logos, and graphics that enhance your organization\'s professional image. With its strong magnetic hold and professional appearance, this badge is perfect for corporate environments, trade shows, and events where quick and secure identification is required. The magnetic backing provides a strong hold that won\'t easily come loose during normal activities while still allowing for easy removal when necessary.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: Durable plastic (PVC or ABS) with magnetic backing\r\n- Dimensions: 75mm x 50mm x 3mm\r\n- Thickness: 3mm standard (including magnetic backing)\r\n- Surface Finish: Smooth, printable surface\r\n- Print Area: Full surface coverage\r\n- Print Compatibility: Compatible with standard badge printers\r\n- Attachment Options: Strong magnetic backing\r\n- Magnetic Strength: Holds securely to metal surfaces\r\n- Durability: Resistant to bending, cracking, and fading\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 85% non-condensing\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general badge standards\r\n- Lifespan: 1-2 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, custom shapes available', 30.00, 'badge-magnetic.png', '2025-11-16 21:25:39', '2025-11-17 00:59:40'),
(21, NULL, 'Standard PVC Card', 'The Standard PVC Card is a reliable and cost-effective identification solution made from high-quality polyvinyl chloride (PVC) material. This standard CR80 sized card (85.6mm x 54mm) is perfect for basic employee ID cards, student identification, membership cards, and access control applications. The card features a smooth surface that accepts standard printing methods, making it easy to customize with logos, text, and basic graphics. The PVC material provides good durability and resistance to everyday wear and tear, ensuring the card maintains its appearance over extended use. With its professional look and affordable price point, this card is ideal for organizations seeking a balance between quality and cost-effectiveness for their identification needs.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: Standard PVC (Polyvinyl Chloride)\r\n- Dimensions: CR80 standard (85.6mm x 54mm x 0.76mm)\r\n- Thickness: 0.76mm (30 mil)\r\n- Surface Finish: Smooth finish on both sides\r\n- Print Compatibility: Compatible with standard card printers\r\n- Operating Temperature: -20°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -30°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: 10% to 90% non-condensing\r\n- Durability: Good resistance to bending and scratching\r\n- Print Area: Full surface coverage on both sides\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: ISO/IEC 7810 ID-1 format\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions', 100.00, 'id-card-pvc.png', '2025-11-16 21:28:49', '2025-11-17 00:57:11'),
(22, NULL, 'Pouch Card Holder', 'The Pouch Card Holder is a protective accessory designed to securely hold and display standard identification cards while providing additional durability and protection. This clear pouch is made from high-quality PVC or PETG material that ensures long-lasting performance and maintains crystal-clear visibility of the enclosed card. The holder features a secure sealing mechanism that prevents cards from falling out while allowing for easy insertion and removal. The pouch design provides protection against moisture, dust, and minor impacts, extending the life of the enclosed ID card. With its standard size compatibility, this pouch holder can accommodate most CR80 sized cards and can be easily attached to lanyards, keychains, or badge clips for convenient carrying.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Pouch Material: Clear PVC or PETG\r\n- Card Compatibility: Standard CR80 size (85.6mm x 54mm)\r\n- Pouch Dimensions: 90mm x 60mm (with sealing margin)\r\n- Thickness: 0.4mm pouch material\r\n- Attachment Options: Lanyard hole, keychain loop\r\n- Print Area: Full visibility of enclosed card\r\n- Durability: Water-resistant and tear-resistant\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +60°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 80% non-condensing\r\n- Security Features: Secure sealing mechanism\r\n- Edge Quality: Heat-sealed edges for durability\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general ID card accessory standards\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions', 80.00, 'id-card-pouch.png', '2025-11-16 21:28:49', '2025-11-17 00:57:11'),
(23, NULL, 'Premium PVC Card', 'The Premium PVC Card is a high-end identification solution crafted from superior-grade polyvinyl chloride (PVC) material for exceptional durability and professional appearance. This standard CR80 sized card (85.6mm x 54mm) is designed for organizations that demand the highest quality identification cards for executive IDs, VIP access cards, and premium membership cards. The card features a premium glossy or matte finish that enhances print quality and provides superior resistance to wear, fading, and environmental factors. The advanced PVC material ensures long-lasting performance with excellent printability on both sides using various printing technologies including UV, dye-sublimation, and laser engraving. With its superior quality and professional appearance, this card is perfect for organizations that want to make a strong impression while providing reliable identification solutions.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: Premium-grade PVC (Polyvinyl Chloride)\r\n- Dimensions: CR80 standard (85.6mm x 54mm x 0.76mm)\r\n- Thickness: 0.76mm (30 mil)\r\n- Surface Finish: Premium glossy or matte options\r\n- Print Compatibility: Compatible with UV, dye-sublimation, and laser printers\r\n- Operating Temperature: -20°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -30°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: 10% to 90% non-condensing\r\n- Durability: Excellent resistance to bending, scratching, and fading\r\n- Print Area: Full surface coverage on both sides\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: ISO/IEC 7810 ID-1 format\r\n- Optional Features: Holographic overlay, magnetic stripe, barcode\r\n- Lifespan: 5-7 years under normal usage conditions', 150.00, 'id-card-uv-printed-pvc.png', '2025-11-16 21:28:49', '2025-11-17 00:57:11'),
(24, NULL, 'Nylon Lanyard with Breakaway', 'The Nylon Lanyard with Breakaway is a premium quality identification accessory made from strong and durable nylon material that offers excellent strength and longevity with added safety features. This lanyard features a smooth, soft texture that is comfortable to wear while providing superior durability and resistance to fraying. The standard 20mm width is ideal for sublimation printing, allowing for vibrant, full-color designs that won\'t fade or crack over time. With an adjustable length, this lanyard is perfect for employee ID cards, visitor passes, and event badges. The durable construction ensures it can withstand daily use in various environments, from corporate offices to industrial settings. The key feature of this lanyard is the integrated breakaway safety mechanism that automatically releases under pressure, providing added security in situations where the lanyard might get caught or pulled. This makes it particularly suitable for environments where safety is a priority, such as schools, hospitals, and industrial facilities.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: High-quality nylon fabric\r\n- Width: 20mm (standard)\r\n- Length: 900mm (adjustable)\r\n- Printing Method: Sublimation printing for vibrant colors\r\n- Color Fastness: Excellent fade resistance\r\n- Durability: Resistant to fraying and wear\r\n- Attachment Options: Breakaway clip, lobster clasp, metal swivel\r\n- Safety Features: Integrated breakaway safety mechanism\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Washability: Hand wash recommended\r\n- Edge Finish: Heat-sealed edges to prevent fraying\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general textile accessory standards\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions', 45.00, 'lanyard_poly.png', '2025-11-16 21:28:49', '2025-11-17 00:59:40'),
(25, NULL, 'Custom Printed Lanyard', 'The Custom Printed Lanyard is a premium identification accessory that offers fully personalized printing to showcase your brand, logo, or message with vibrant colors and sharp details. This printed lanyard is made from premium polyester or nylon material that ensures durability and long-lasting performance. Using advanced sublimation printing technology, we create full-color designs that won\'t fade, crack, or peel over time, even with regular use and washing. Our printing process allows for complete customization, including your company logo, tagline, artwork, or any graphics that represent your brand identity. The lanyard features a smooth, soft texture that is comfortable to wear while providing superior strength and resistance to fraying. With a standard width of 20mm and adjustable length, this printed lanyard is perfect for employee ID cards, visitor passes, event badges, and promotional giveaways. Available with various attachment options including breakaway clips, lobster clasps, and metal swivels for added safety and convenience.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: High-quality polyester or nylon fabric\r\n- Width: 20mm (standard)\r\n- Length: 900mm (adjustable)\r\n- Printing Method: Sublimation printing for vibrant colors\r\n- Color Fastness: Excellent fade resistance\r\n- Durability: Resistant to fraying and wear\r\n- Attachment Options: Breakaway clip, lobster clasp, metal swivel\r\n- Safety Features: Breakaway release mechanism available\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +50°C\r\n- Washability: Hand wash recommended\r\n- Edge Finish: Heat-sealed edges to prevent fraying\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general textile accessory standards\r\n- Lifespan: 2-3 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, logo placement', 65.00, 'lanyard_print.png', '2025-11-16 21:28:49', '2025-11-17 00:59:40'),
(26, NULL, 'Clip-On Badge Holder', 'The Clip-On Badge Holder is a versatile and practical accessory designed to securely hold and display standard identification badges while providing convenient attachment to clothing, uniforms, or lanyards. This holder features a sturdy plastic construction with a reliable clip mechanism that ensures your badge stays in place during daily activities. The clear design maintains full visibility of the enclosed badge while providing protection against wear, moisture, and minor impacts. The compact 75x50mm size accommodates most standard badges and ID cards, making it ideal for employee identification, visitor passes, and event credentials. The smooth surface can also be customized with printing if needed. With its lightweight design and secure clip attachment, this badge holder is perfect for corporate environments, healthcare facilities, educational institutions, and events where quick and easy identification is required.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: Clear durable plastic (PVC or PETG)\r\n- Dimensions: 80mm x 55mm x 2mm (with badge accommodation)\r\n- Thickness: 2mm standard\r\n- Surface Finish: Clear, smooth finish\r\n- Attachment Options: Secure clip-on mechanism\r\n- Durability: Resistant to bending, cracking, and fading\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 85% non-condensing\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general badge accessory standards\r\n- Lifespan: 1-2 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Optional printing available', 25.00, 'badge_plastic.png', '2025-11-16 21:28:49', '2025-11-17 01:02:09'),
(27, NULL, 'Magnetic Badge Holder', 'The Magnetic Badge Holder is a premium identification accessory that utilizes a strong magnetic attachment system for secure and convenient wear. This holder features a sturdy plastic construction with a powerful magnetic backing that provides a reliable hold to metal surfaces while allowing for easy removal when needed. The clear design maintains full visibility of the enclosed badge while providing protection against wear, moisture, and minor impacts. The compact 75x50mm size accommodates most standard badges and ID cards, making it ideal for employee identification, visitor passes, and event credentials. The smooth surface can also be customized with printing if needed. With its strong magnetic hold and professional appearance, this badge holder is perfect for corporate environments, trade shows, and events where quick and secure identification is required. The magnetic backing provides a strong hold that won\'t easily come loose during normal activities while still allowing for easy removal when necessary.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: Clear durable plastic (PVC or PETG) with magnetic backing\r\n- Dimensions: 80mm x 55mm x 3mm (including magnetic backing)\r\n- Thickness: 3mm standard\r\n- Surface Finish: Clear, smooth finish\r\n- Attachment Options: Strong magnetic backing\r\n- Magnetic Strength: Holds securely to metal surfaces\r\n- Durability: Resistant to bending, cracking, and fading\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 85% non-condensing\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general badge accessory standards\r\n- Lifespan: 1-2 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Optional printing available', 30.00, 'badge_plastic.png', '2025-11-16 21:28:49', '2025-11-17 01:02:09'),
