(31, NULL, 'Plastic Badges', 'The Plastic Badges are durable and professional identification solutions designed for temporary or permanent use in various environments. These badges feature a sturdy plastic construction that resists bending, cracking, and fading, ensuring long-lasting performance. The compact 75x50mm size makes them ideal for attaching to uniforms, clothing, or lanyards while maintaining visibility. The smooth surface accepts high-quality printing, allowing for clear text, logos, and graphics that enhance your organization\'s professional image. With their lightweight design and secure attachment options, these badges are perfect for employee identification, visitor passes, and event credentials. The plastic material is easy to clean and maintain, making it suitable for use in healthcare, hospitality, retail, and industrial settings. Available in bulk quantities with various attachment methods including clips, pins, and magnetic backs for versatile application.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: Durable plastic (PVC or ABS)\r\n- Dimensions: 75mm x 50mm x 2mm\r\n- Thickness: 2mm standard\r\n- Surface Finish: Smooth, printable surface\r\n- Print Area: Full surface coverage\r\n- Print Compatibility: Compatible with standard badge printers\r\n- Attachment Options: Clip, pin, magnetic back available\r\n- Durability: Resistant to bending, cracking, and fading\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 85% non-condensing\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general badge standards\r\n- Lifespan: 1-2 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, bulk quantities available', 35.00, 'badge_plastic.png', '2025-11-16 21:33:31', '2025-11-17 01:02:09'),
(32, NULL, 'Clip Badges', 'The Clip Badges are versatile and durable identification solutions designed for temporary or permanent use in various environments. These badges feature a sturdy plastic construction with integrated clip mechanisms that allow for easy attachment and removal from clothing, uniforms, or lanyards. The compact design makes them ideal for visitor passes, event credentials, and temporary identification needs. The smooth surface accepts high-quality printing, allowing for clear text, logos, and graphics that enhance your organization\'s professional image. With their lightweight design and secure clip attachment, these badges are perfect for situations where quick and easy identification is needed. The plastic material is easy to clean and maintain, making it suitable for use in healthcare, hospitality, retail, and industrial settings. Available in bulk quantities for cost-effective solutions.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: Durable plastic (PVC or ABS)\r\n- Dimensions: 75mm x 50mm x 2mm\r\n- Thickness: 2mm standard\r\n- Surface Finish: Smooth, printable surface\r\n- Print Area: Full surface coverage\r\n- Print Compatibility: Compatible with standard badge printers\r\n- Attachment Options: Integrated clip mechanism\r\n- Durability: Resistant to bending, cracking, and fading\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 85% non-condensing\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general badge standards\r\n- Lifespan: 1-2 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, bulk quantities available', 25.00, 'badge_plastic.png', '2025-11-16 21:33:31', '2025-11-17 01:02:09'),
(33, NULL, 'Magnetic Badges', 'The Magnetic Badges are premium identification solutions that utilize a powerful magnetic attachment system for secure and convenient wear. These badges feature a sturdy plastic construction with strong magnetic backing that provides a reliable hold to metal surfaces while allowing for easy removal when needed. The compact 75x50mm size makes them ideal for employee identification, visitor passes, and event credentials. The smooth surface accepts high-quality printing, allowing for clear text, logos, and graphics that enhance your organization\'s professional image. With their strong magnetic hold and professional appearance, these badges are perfect for corporate environments, trade shows, and events where quick and secure identification is required. The magnetic backing provides a strong hold that won\'t easily come loose during normal activities while still allowing for easy removal when necessary. Available in bulk quantities for cost-effective solutions.\r\n\r\nSpecifications:\r\n- Material: Durable plastic (PVC or ABS) with magnetic backing\r\n- Dimensions: 75mm x 50mm x 3mm\r\n- Thickness: 3mm standard (including magnetic backing)\r\n- Surface Finish: Smooth, printable surface\r\n- Print Area: Full surface coverage\r\n- Print Compatibility: Compatible with standard badge printers\r\n- Attachment Options: Strong magnetic backing\r\n- Magnetic Strength: Holds securely to metal surfaces\r\n- Durability: Resistant to bending, cracking, and fading\r\n- Operating Temperature: -10°C to +60°C\r\n- Storage Temperature: -20°C to +70°C\r\n- Humidity Resistance: Up to 85% non-condensing\r\n- Edge Quality: Precision cut with smooth edges\r\n- Standards Compliance: Meets general badge standards\r\n- Lifespan: 1-2 years under normal usage conditions\r\n- Customization: Full-color printing, bulk quantities available', 30.00, 'badge_plastic.png', '2025-11-16 21:33:31', '2025-11-17 01:02:09'),
(34, 4, 'School Management System', 'Transform your school\'s operations with the **Simption School Management System**, a comprehensive ERP solution designed to streamline every aspect of academic and administrative management. Our powerful, user-friendly software empowers educators to focus on what matters most—providing quality education—while automating and simplifying complex administrative tasks.\n\nFrom student admission and fee collection to examination management and report card generation, our all-in-one platform provides a centralized system for all your school\'s needs. The integrated modules for library, hostel, and transport management ensure that every department is connected and working in harmony.\n\nEmbrace the future of education with our advanced features, including RFID and biometric attendance, live bus tracking, and dedicated mobile apps for students, parents, and staff. Our online learning platform, complete with e-learning modules and online exams, makes it easy to transition to a blended learning environment.\n\nWith the Simption School Management System, you can improve communication with parents through our integrated bulk SMS and push notification system, ensuring they are always up-to-date on their child\'s progress. Our robust security features and reliable 24/7 support provide peace of mind, knowing that your data is safe and that help is always just a call or click away.\n\nJoin the 6200+ schools that trust Simption to simplify their management, enhance their productivity, and create a better learning environment for their students.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_school_management.png', '2025-11-16 21:52:43', '2025-11-16 21:52:43'),
(35, 4, 'RFID & Face Recognition Attendance System', 'Modernize your attendance tracking with the **Simption RFID & Face Recognition Attendance System**. This powerful, dual-technology solution combines the speed and convenience of RFID cards with the security and accuracy of biometric face recognition, providing a seamless and foolproof way to manage attendance for students and staff.\n\nOur advanced system features a high-precision dual-lens camera with infrared capabilities, ensuring reliable face detection even in low-light conditions. The integrated RFID reader provides a quick and easy alternative for card-based check-ins. With real-time data synchronization to the central School Management ERP, you can monitor attendance, generate reports, and manage users from a single, user-friendly dashboard.\n\nOne of the standout features of our system is the instant SMS and push notification alerts sent to parents the moment their child enters or leaves the school premises. This provides an extra layer of security and peace of mind for parents, knowing that their child is safe and accounted for.\n\nThe Simption RFID & Face Recognition Attendance System is more than just an attendance tool; it\'s a complete access control solution. With its robust hardware and intelligent software, you can manage access to different areas of your campus, ensuring that only authorized individuals can enter restricted zones.\n\nUpgrade to a smarter, more secure, and more efficient way to manage attendance with the Simption RFID & Face Recognition Attendance System.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_attendance_system.png', '2025-11-16 21:53:39', '2025-11-16 21:53:39'),
(36, 4, 'Live Bus Tracking System', 'Ensure the safety and security of your students with the **Simption Live Bus Tracking System**. Our advanced GPS tracking solution provides real-time visibility into your entire fleet of school buses, giving you complete control and peace of mind.\n\nWith our intuitive web-based dashboard and dedicated mobile app, you can monitor the exact location of each bus, track its speed, and view its route history. The integrated parent app allows parents to track their child\'s bus in real-time, so they know exactly when to expect their child at the bus stop.\n\nOur Live Bus Tracking System is more than just a tracking tool; it\'s a complete fleet management solution. With features like route optimization, geofencing, and over-speeding alerts, you can improve the efficiency of your transport operations and ensure the safety of your students.\n\nThe system also provides detailed reports on distance traveled, stoppage time, and fuel consumption, helping you to reduce costs and improve the overall performance of your fleet.\n\nChoose the Simption Live Bus Tracking System for a smarter, safer, and more efficient way to manage your school\'s transportation.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_bus_tracking.png', '2025-11-16 21:54:34', '2025-11-16 21:54:34'),
(37, 4, 'Android Apps for School Management', 'Stay connected with your school community like never before with the **Simption Android Apps for School Management**. Our suite of dedicated mobile applications for students, parents, teachers, and administrators brings the power of our School Management System to your fingertips.\n\n**For Students & Parents:**\nThe Student/Parent App provides a one-stop solution for all your academic needs. View attendance records, check homework assignments, access report cards, pay fees online, and stay informed about important school events and announcements.\n\n**For Teachers:**\nThe Teacher App empowers educators to manage their daily tasks with ease. Mark attendance, upload homework, enter student marks, and communicate with parents, all from the convenience of your mobile device.\n\n**For Administrators:**\nThe Administrator App provides a bird\'s-eye view of your entire school\'s operations. Access key data, monitor staff and student activity, and send school-wide announcements on the go.\n\n**For Bus Drivers:**\nThe Bus Driver App streamlines your daily routes with features like student lists, pickup/drop-off points, and route navigation.\n\nWith our secure, user-friendly, and feature-rich Android apps, you can enhance communication, improve transparency, and create a more connected and engaged school community.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_android_apps.png', '2025-11-16 21:55:31', '2025-11-16 21:55:31'),
(38, 4, 'Online Academic Features', 'Embrace the future of education with the **Simption Online Academic Features**, a powerful e-learning platform that seamlessly integrates with our School Management System. Our suite of online tools empowers educators to create engaging and interactive learning experiences for students, whether they are in the classroom or at home.\n\n**Live Classes:**\nConduct live, interactive classes with our built-in video conferencing solution. Share your screen, use the digital whiteboard, and engage with students in real-time, just as you would in a traditional classroom.\n\n**Online Exams:**\nCreate and conduct secure online exams with ease. Our flexible exam module supports a variety of question types, from multiple-choice and true/false to short answer and essay questions. With automated grading and detailed performance analytics, you can save time and gain valuable insights into your students\' learning.\n\n**Smart Classes & Video Tutorials:**\nBring your lessons to life with our rich library of digital content. Our Smart Classes feature includes engaging videos, animations, and interactive simulations that make learning fun and effective. You can also upload and share your own video tutorials for students to access anytime, anywhere.\n\nWith the Simption Online Academic Features, you can create a flexible, engaging, and effective learning environment that meets the needs of today\'s students.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_online_features.png', '2025-11-16 21:56:28', '2025-11-16 21:56:28'),
(39, 4, 'Bulk SMS Service', 'Reach your audience instantly and effectively with the **Simption Bulk SMS Service**. Our reliable and high-speed SMS gateway allows you to send thousands of messages per second, making it the perfect solution for all your communication needs.\n\n**Transactional SMS:**\nKeep your users informed with our transactional SMS service. Send important alerts, notifications, and one-time passwords (OTPs) with high-speed delivery and guaranteed reliability.\n\n**Promotional SMS:**\nPromote your products and services with our promotional SMS service. Reach thousands of potential customers with a single click and track the performance of your campaigns with our real-time delivery reports.\n\n**Easy Integration:**\nOur developer-friendly API makes it easy to integrate SMS functionality into your own applications. Whether you\'re a school looking to improve parent communication or a business looking to run a marketing campaign, our Bulk SMS Service has you covered.\n\nChoose the Simption Bulk SMS Service for a reliable, affordable, and effective way to communicate with your audience.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_bulk_sms.png', '2025-11-16 21:57:38', '2025-11-16 21:57:38'),
(40, 4, 'Student Management', 'The **Simption Student Management** module is a powerful and comprehensive Student Information System (SIS) that simplifies and automates all aspects of student administration. From online admissions to graduation, our module provides a centralized platform to manage the entire student lifecycle.\n\nWith our intuitive interface, you can easily manage student admissions, create detailed student profiles, track daily and subject-wise attendance, and maintain academic records. The module also includes a robust communication system that allows you to send individual or group messages to students and parents, ensuring that everyone stays informed.\n\nThe Student Management module seamlessly integrates with all other modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_student_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:31:14', '2025-11-16 22:31:14'),
(41, 4, 'Staff Management', 'The **Simption Staff Management** module is a complete Human Resource Management System (HRMS) designed to simplify and automate all aspects of staff administration. From recruitment to retirement, our module provides a centralized platform to manage the entire employee lifecycle.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can easily maintain employee records, automate payroll processing, manage leave requests, and track employee performance. The module also includes a powerful reporting system that provides valuable insights into your workforce.\n\nThe Staff Management module seamlessly integrates with the Attendance Management and other modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_staff_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:31:39', '2025-11-16 22:31:39'),
(42, 4, 'Account Management', 'The **Simption Account Management** module is a comprehensive financial accounting solution designed to simplify and automate all aspects of school finance. From fee collection to financial reporting, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your financial transactions.\n\nWith our intuitive interface, you can easily manage fee structures, track expenses, maintain a general ledger, and generate a variety of financial reports. The module also includes a powerful dashboard that provides a real-time overview of your school\'s financial health.\n\nThe Account Management module seamlessly integrates with the Fee Management and other modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_account_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:32:03', '2025-11-16 22:32:03'),
(43, 4, 'Admission Management', 'The **Simption Admission Management** module is a complete online admission solution that simplifies and automates the entire admission process. From application submission to enrollment, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your admission-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can easily create customizable online application forms, securely manage document uploads, track the status of all applications, and automatically generate merit lists. The module also includes a powerful communication system that allows you to send automated emails and SMS alerts to applicants.\n\nThe Admission Management module seamlessly integrates with the Student Management and other modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_admission_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:32:29', '2025-11-16 22:32:29'),
(44, 4, 'Principal Desk', 'The **Simption Principal Desk** is a powerful and intuitive dashboard that provides a 360-degree view of your entire school\'s operations. Designed specifically for school principals and administrators, our module provides a centralized platform to monitor, manage, and communicate with your entire school community.\n\nWith our real-time analytics, you can get instant insights into student attendance, staff performance, and financial data. The communication hub allows you to send announcements, circulars, and messages to staff, students, and parents with a single click. The module also includes a powerful report generation tool that allows you to create a variety of reports for analysis and decision-making.\n\nThe Principal Desk seamlessly integrates with all other modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_principal_desk.png', '2025-11-16 22:32:53', '2025-11-16 22:32:53'),
(45, 4, 'Fees Management', 'The **Simption Fees Management** module is a comprehensive fee collection and management system that simplifies and automates the entire fee management process. From creating fee structures to generating fee reports, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your fee-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can easily create and manage different fee structures, collect fees online through multiple payment gateways, send automated fee reminders to parents, and generate a variety of reports on fee collections, dues, and defaulters.\n\nThe Fees Management module seamlessly integrates with the Account Management and other modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_fees_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:33:16', '2025-11-16 22:33:16'),
(46, 4, 'ID Card Generation', 'The **Simption ID Card Generation** module is a powerful and easy-to-use ID card design and printing software that simplifies the entire ID card creation process. From designing professional ID cards to printing them in bulk, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your ID card-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly drag-and-drop designer, you can create professional-looking ID cards in minutes. The module automatically fetches student and staff data from the database, so you don\'t have to worry about manual data entry. You can also add barcodes and QR codes to your ID cards for easy scanning.\n\nThe ID Card Generation module seamlessly integrates with the Student Management and Staff Management modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_id_card_generation.png', '2025-11-16 22:33:42', '2025-11-16 22:33:42'),
(47, 4, 'Marksheet Generation', 'The **Simption Marksheet Generation** module is a powerful and easy-to-use examination and marksheet software that simplifies the entire marksheet creation process. From creating exams and entering marks to generating and printing professional-looking marksheets, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your exam-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can easily create and manage different exams and grading systems, enter and manage student marks, and automatically generate and print professional-looking marksheets. The module also allows you to create and customize report cards with student photos, grades, and teacher comments.\n\nThe Marksheet Generation module seamlessly integrates with the Student Management and other modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_marksheet_generation.png', '2025-11-16 22:34:11', '2025-11-16 22:34:11'),
(48, 4, 'Time Table Management', 'The **Simption Time Table Management** module is a powerful and easy-to-use timetable scheduling software that simplifies the entire timetable creation process. From automatically generating a balanced and clash-free timetable to making manual adjustments with a drag-and-drop interface, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your timetable-related tasks.\n\nWith our intelligent algorithm, you can automatically generate a timetable for the entire institution in minutes. The module takes into account teacher availability, classroom capacity, and other constraints to create an optimized and efficient timetable. You can also easily make manual adjustments to the timetable with our user-friendly drag-and-drop interface.\n\nThe Time Table Management module seamlessly integrates with the Student Management and Staff Management modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_time_table_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:34:38', '2025-11-16 22:34:38'),
(49, 4, 'Certificate Generation', 'The **Simption Certificate Generation** module is a powerful and easy-to-use certificate design and generation software that simplifies the entire certificate creation process. From designing professional certificates to generating them in bulk, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your certificate-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly drag-and-drop designer, you can create professional-looking certificates in minutes. The module automatically fetches student and staff data from the database, so you don\'t have to worry about manual data entry. You can also create and save your own certificate templates for future use.\n\nThe Certificate Generation module seamlessly integrates with the Student Management and Staff Management modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_certificate_generation.png', '2025-11-16 22:35:05', '2025-11-16 22:35:05'),
(50, 4, 'TC (Transfer Certificate) Generation', 'The **Simption TC (Transfer Certificate) Generation** module is a powerful and easy-to-use software that simplifies the entire TC creation process. From automatically generating TCs with all the required information to printing them in bulk, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your TC-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can automatically generate TCs in minutes. The module automatically fetches student data from the database, so you don\'t have to worry about manual data entry. You can also create and save your own TC templates for future use.\n\nThe TC Generation module seamlessly integrates with the Student Management module of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_tc_generation.png', '2025-11-16 22:35:34', '2025-11-16 22:35:34'),
(51, 4, 'Admit Card Generation', 'The **Simption Admit Card Generation** module is a powerful and easy-to-use software that simplifies the entire admit card creation process. From automatically generating admit cards with all the required information to printing them in bulk, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your admit card-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can automatically generate admit cards in minutes. The module automatically fetches student data from the database, so you don\'t have to worry about manual data entry. You can also create and save your own admit card templates for future use.\n\nThe Admit Card Generation module seamlessly integrates with the Student Management and Examination modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_admit_card_generation.png', '2025-11-16 22:36:03', '2025-11-16 22:36:03'),
(52, 4, 'Homework Management', 'The **Simption Homework Management** module is a powerful and easy-to-use homework and assignment management system that simplifies the entire homework process. From creating and assigning homework to grading and providing feedback, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your homework-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, teachers can easily create and assign homework with attachments and deadlines. Students can submit their homework online, and teachers can track the status of homework submission for all students. The module also allows teachers to grade homework and provide feedback to students.\n\nThe Homework Management module seamlessly integrates with the Student Management and Teacher App modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_homework_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:36:32', '2025-11-16 22:36:32'),
(53, 4, 'Question Paper Management', 'The **Simption Question Paper Management** module is a powerful and easy-to-use question bank and exam paper generator that simplifies the entire question paper creation process. From creating a large repository of questions to automatically generating question papers, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your exam paper-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can easily create and manage a question bank with different difficulty levels and topics. The module allows you to automatically generate question papers based on predefined templates and question selection criteria. You can also print question papers directly or export them to PDF and Word formats.\n\nThe Question Paper Management module seamlessly integrates with the Examination and Online Exam modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_question_paper_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:37:01', '2025-11-16 22:37:01'),
(54, 4, 'Hostel Management', 'The **Simption Hostel Management** module is a comprehensive hostel and accommodation management system that simplifies and automates all aspects of hostel administration. From room allocation to mess management, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your hostel-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can easily allocate rooms to students, manage mess menus and billing, track visitors, and monitor student attendance in the hostel. The module also includes a powerful reporting system that provides valuable insights into your hostel\'s operations.\n\nThe Hostel Management module seamlessly integrates with the Student Management and Fees Management modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_hostel_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:37:35', '2025-11-16 22:37:35'),
(55, 4, 'Library Management', 'The **Simption Library Management** module is a complete library automation system that simplifies and automates all aspects of library administration. From book cataloging to circulation management, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your library-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can easily create and manage a comprehensive catalog of all your books, manage book issues and returns, and automatically calculate and manage fines for overdue books. The module also includes an Online Public Access Catalog (OPAC) that allows students and staff to search for books online.\n\nThe Library Management module seamlessly integrates with the Student Management and Staff Management modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_library_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:38:13', '2025-11-16 22:38:13'),
(56, 4, 'Downloads Management', 'The **Simption Downloads Management** module is a powerful and easy-to-use content and document sharing platform that simplifies the entire content sharing process. From uploading and organizing content to controlling access and tracking downloads, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your content sharing-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can easily upload and share a variety of content, including documents, videos, and presentations. You can organize content into folders and subfolders for easy access, and you can control who can access and download content based on user roles. The module also allows you to track who has downloaded which content and when.\n\nThe Downloads Management module seamlessly integrates with the Student Management and Staff Management modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_downloads_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:38:41', '2025-11-16 22:38:41'),
(57, 4, 'Stocks Management', 'The **Simption Stocks Management** module is a powerful and easy-to-use inventory and stock management system that simplifies the entire stock management process. From creating and managing a comprehensive list of all your stock items to generating a variety of reports on stock levels, consumption, and purchases, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your stock-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can easily create and manage a comprehensive list of all your stock items, track the quantity of each item in stock, create and manage purchase orders for new stock, and generate a variety of reports on stock levels, consumption, and purchases.\n\nThe Stocks Management module seamlessly integrates with the Account Management module of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_stocks_management.png', '2025-11-16 22:39:10', '2025-11-16 22:39:10'),
(58, 4, 'User Creation', 'The **Simption User Creation** module is a powerful and easy-to-use user and role management system that simplifies the entire user management process. From creating and managing user accounts to controlling user access to different modules and features of the ERP system, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your user-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can easily create, manage, and disable user accounts for students, staff, and parents. You can also create and manage different user roles with different permissions, and you can control user access to different modules and features of the ERP system. The module also includes an audit trail that tracks all user activity in the system.\n\nThe User Creation module seamlessly integrates with all other modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_user_creation.png', '2025-11-16 22:39:33', '2025-11-16 22:39:33'),
(59, 4, 'Online Results', 'The **Simption Online Results** module is a powerful and easy-to-use online result publication system that simplifies the entire result publication process. From publishing exam results online to providing a graphical analysis of student performance, our module provides a centralized platform to manage all your result-related tasks.\n\nWith our user-friendly interface, you can easily publish exam results online for students and parents to view. Students can securely access their results with a unique username and password, and they can view detailed marksheets with subject-wise marks and grades. The module also provides a graphical analysis of student performance over time.\n\nThe Online Results module seamlessly integrates with the Marksheet Generation and Student App modules of the Simption School Management ERP, providing a unified and efficient solution for your institution.\n\n**Buy Link:** `https://simption.com/`', 0.00, 'erp_online_results.png', '2025-11-16 22:39:55', '2025-11-16 22:39:55'),
